title: Star Wars Republic Commando Mac
description:
Game works perfect and smoothly.
My Mac specs : MacBook Pro 13-inch Late 2011
Memory : 4 GB
Graphics : Intel HD Graphics 384 MB
Running on OS X Mountain Lion 10.8
Known Problems : Character's skin is greenish yellow.
Fix : Set Bumpmapping Quality to "LOW" in game options.
Enjoy the game and don't forget to SEED SEED SEED !!!
Email me if you have a problem and I will help :)
